== SYNOPSIS

*vpi4r* ['OPTIONS'] 'COMMAND' ['ARGUMENT'] ...

=== Command

[horizontal]
translate:: Converts Verilog `defines, constants, ranges, etc. into Ruby.
generate:: Creates test skeletons from Verilog 2001/1995 module declarations.
simulate:: Executes the given tests using the given Verilog simulator.

=== Options

*-h*, *--help*::
  Display this manual and exit.

*-v*, *--version*::
  Print version number and exit.

=== Examples

  vpi4r translate

  vpi4r generate

  vpi4r simulate files=FILE_GLOB using=SIMULATOR
